{"type": "article", "id": 41269, "title": "这个智能“口袋”，想把你的手机变成拍立得｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-05-25T23:26:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 33032, "name": "Dress Code"}, {"id": 40828, "name": "Prynt"}, {"id": 40829, "name": "Elements Optimal"}, {"id": 40830, "name": "Guy Laramée"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 256, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170525231611umn8rpw5xJZUHgSO.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Prynt Pocket by Prynt</h3><p>用手机记录生活时，你有没有想过当场冲印出充满回忆的相片？2015 年，来自旧金山的初创公司 Prynt 就推出了具有这一功能的同名手机壳，除了保护手机之外，它还是一个可以让手机变身为拍立得的便携式照片打印机。使用配套的 App 进行拍摄时，你还可以录制一段最长 10 秒的视频，之后便能通过 App 中的 AR 技术让相片动起来了。最近，Prynt 又推出了一款名为 Prynt Pocket 的配件，和占据整个手机背部的保护壳相比，可以一手掌握的 Pocket 更容易让人联想到拍立得相机。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.prynt.co/en/shop#/products/pryntpockets\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 149.99 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231652DmR2Cwu7cEto5U9F.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705252316518qt3UxkWSrPphI2B.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231651Cqi7G5VouwBMQR80.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231651C3Ltwa0qzKbHTmFZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Mellow by Creatio</h3><p>挑选音响时你有没有因为地方太小或者追求整体风格协调而苦恼过？美国设计团队 Creatio 为此将边桌、音响和充电功能结合在一起，带来了这款名为 Mellow 的智能家具。它通过蓝牙和播放设备绑定，有效范围最远可达 10 米。在没有外接电源的情况下，内置的锂电池（6600 毫安时）可以在最大音量下连续播放 3 小时。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/creatiodesign/mellow\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 289 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231908ueqy8wxbtJWzr20E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231908HPjYOBc3LCiqI9uT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231908kHMaGRgCOosZLwf7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.739706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231908duZaUKX16IbP7NAD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Animal Chairs by Takeshi Sawada</h3><p>日本设计师 <a href=\"http://kamina-c.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Takeshi Sawada</a> 最近为丹麦设计公司 <a href=\"http://eo.dk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Elements Optimal</a> 打造了三款动物造型的儿童椅。利用温润的木料和圆鼓鼓的坐垫，Sawada 成功还原出了简化版的小鹿斑比、绵羊和牛，非常可爱。这是它们的<a href=\"http://eo.dk/webshop/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 249 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231856ei6Mntu5GrKTzVmZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.616250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231856DIjnMeTh0qB8CPuS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.160000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231856ON0rKFTbZ7hoyEip.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.889333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705252318565A0kwW8VSBI1mCzp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.138667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>My. Docs by Brobygrafiska Team</h3><p>在发现很多电子产品都会使用一次性的塑料包装后，瑞典设计团队 <a href=\"http://brobygrafiska.se/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Brobygrafiska</a> 决定从移动硬盘的入手，开发了一款可以当作保护壳重复使用的概念包装 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/42681907/External-hard-drive-packaging\" rel=\"nofollow\">My. Docs</a>。他们在纸板盒内部预留了放置连接线的分区，并且让连接线通过顶端的两个小窗口穿过，形成一个简易的提手。纸盒的内外都预留了可以标注信息的区域，便于整理。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231834lL5f9E6gdKorR37w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231834c2JHmAGIoCVizwX9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.681667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231834iRYcUPLH2IkB6n3o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.693750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231834J60H3j9Q1sTkRB84.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231834FZqi4WglEPzyXoNt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.747500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Coke Habit by Dress Code</h3><p>你还记得小时候沉迷或是令自己上瘾的事物吗？最近，美国纽约的制片公司 <a href=\"http://dresscodeny.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dress Code</a> 根据一名员工在童年时期喝可乐成瘾的经历，制作了一段名为 Coke Habit 的动画短片。动画采用了象征可口可乐的红白以及黑色，用超现实的手法描绘了上瘾后的身心变化。如果你感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/217841404\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>观看全片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231956MJVnFogly1xiH2K7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.526895\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231956VfyHIeklUwtnpbMm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.526895\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231956uHlCkLfx9DJPAIpt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.526895\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705252319572giJZHUKNGXCFDLv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.526895\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231957r72WXCQevK0uG5kA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.526895\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Craved Books by Guy Laramée</h3><p>现居加拿大蒙特利尔的 <a href=\"http://www.guylaramee.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Guy Laramée</a> 是一名擅长对中古书籍进行改造的艺术家，他会将它们排列在一起，再采用喷砂工艺进行雕刻。经过精细的上色后，这些陈旧的辞典和百科全书就变成了逼真的山川，部分细节的特写照就像是实地的航拍。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231751fbCFaoKYsdx357Wp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.886000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705252317523bD5SUAXZhMzOcYQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.845000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231751l9bNX6Ue1FWIjMrs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.616000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170525231751vJ3qPQ8lDfjtzSaF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705252317520OQUeoLZTYfn9D4p.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.664000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div>"}